# Connect Project to Supabase

## Goal Description
Connect the Next.js application to Supabase to enable database interactions and authentication.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> You will need to provide your `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL` and `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`.

## Proposed Changes

### Dependencies
- Install `@supabase/supabase-js`

### Configuration
#### [NEW] [.env.local](file:///c:/Users/HPPAVILION/Documents/Shop_nextJs/my-app/.env.local)
- Add Supabase URL and Anon Key variables.

#### [MODIFY] [client.ts](file:///c:/Users/HPPAVILION/Documents/Shop_nextJs/my-app/lib/supabase/client.ts)
